%% Diagram: Sequence CRDT interleaving problem
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    S0["Initial: Hello | World"]
    subgraph Concurrent["Concurrent edits at the same position"]
        direction TB
        A["User A types: foo"]
        B["User B types: bar"]
    end
    S0 --> Concurrent
    Concurrent --> BAD["Naive / Logoot worst case<br/><b>Hellofboaor World</b><br/>characters interleaved"]
    Concurrent --> OK1["RGA (timestamp-ordered)<br/><b>HellofoobarWorld</b> or<br/><b>HellobarfooWorld</b>"]
    Concurrent --> BEST["Fugue / Eg-walker<br/>provably never interleaves<br/>distinct concurrent runs"]
